data.meta_site_name: Office of Superintendent of Public Instruction
data.text:
You can apply or renew your certification in this section if you are a Teacher or CTE Applicant.

In-State Program Completer Applicants

Full and Limited certificates you may apply for if you are completing or have completed a state of Washington approved teacher preparation program.

Out-of-State Applicants

Full and Limited certificates you may apply for if you have completed an out-of-state teacher preparation program.

Foreign Trained Applicants

Full certificates you may apply for if you earned your degree outside the U.S.

Already Washington Certified Educators

Full and Limited certificates you may apply for if you have previously held or currently hold a Washington Teaching Certificate.

Career and Technical Education

Full and Limited certificates you may apply for if you are looking to gain or have already held a Career Tech Certification.
